OL,3,CAnguish and outrage: Remembering the
OL,4,Cdrowned valley of Tryweryn 60 years on
OL,6,FIt was in 1955 that Liverpool Council
OL,7,Ffirst announced its intention to build
OL,8,Fa reservoir in the Tryweryn Valley. It
OL,9,Fsaid it needed additional supplies of
OL,10,Fwater to regenerate and redevelop the
OL,11,Fcity after the Second World War. The
OL,12,Fresidents of Capel Celyn were taken
OL,13,Fcompletely by surprise.
