OL,3,CAnguish and outrage: Remembering the
OL,4,Cdrowned valley of Tryweryn 60 years on
OL,6,F"When we were in school I remember
OL,7,Fthat a lot of people - councillors,
OL,8,FMPs and what have you - used to tell
OL,9,Fus as kids: 'don't worry, your homes
OL,10,Fwill be saved'. But that was just
OL,11,Fsomething to keep a child happy I
OL,12,Fsuppose."
OL,14,FDespite furious protests in Wales,
OL,15,Fpetitions to Parliament and
OL,16,Fimpassioned marches on the streets of
OL,17,FLiverpool, the village was razed to
OL,18,Fthe ground and 800 acres of land were
OL,19,Fsubmerged.
